This client library allows you to train Smart Adaptive Recommendations (SAR) models based on transaction history. It also allows you to get item-to-item recommendations and personalized recommendations based on the transactions of a specific user. 
While the client library can be used on its own, it was created to power the recommendations preconfigured solution (http://aka.ms/recotemplate).
This project is dependent on at least the following projects:
A modified version of zlib (https://github.com/madler/zlib)
LightLDA (https://github.com/Microsoft/LightLDA)
